lonely and scared and this whole thing...

432
00:41:53,387 --> 00:41:55,306
is terribly confusing.

433
00:41:57,934 --> 00:41:59,268
Believe me, I know.

434
00:42:01,271 --> 00:42:03,106
But everything about you that's you,

435
00:42:03,773 --> 00:42:08,193
